name: {DD} Reach around, handjob from behind
description:
Again, I couldn't merge it with this Lora without mutations. A pose is quite tricky, so expect 1-2 decent images per generation of 10. These tags might help:

Tags

1boy, male focus, reach-around, reacharound, hand on penis, female behind man

Expect to see lots of traps, and futas - AI is strugling with understaning what goes where in these pose. Putting them in the negative prompts could help. Maybe. Maybe not)

Enjoy)

Feel free to ask any questions here in comments, or in my discord channel.

Also I am making games with AI arts. They will be free in the future, but if you want to participate in making or have an early access - you can support me on patreon)
